            <lg xml:id="TK187">
<l>pakaccollik kēḷirp pirippar nakaccolli</l>
<l>naṭpāṭa ṟēṟṟā tavar</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who know not to live in friendship with amusing conversation will by back-biting estrange even their relatives.</l>
